Martix Of attack data

Martix of Attack Data :: Cohesive Solution

Features

  • https://nixos.wiki/wiki/Overview_of_the_Nix_Language Nix Lang based
  • https://github.com/divnix/POP POP :: Pure Object support
  • https://github.com/divnix/std Std Framework control
  • A flexible https://github.com/divnix/data-merge data-merge(minimal DSL) support
  • Having a resourceful https://github.com/GTrunSec/cells-lab/tree/main/nix cells-lab data point
  • Linking your diagram with any typed data via https://github.com/GTrunSec/structurizr2nix structurizr2nix
  • Using grafonnix https://github.com/divnix/grafonnix and grafonnix-guard https://github.com/GTrunSec/grafonnix-guard can quickly assist you in implementing complex visual security data dashboards/events, and most importantly, you would be able to use the nix lang to link them together(like relationship links).

CI

  • jsonschema check
  • vast-integration check
  • cargo-make CLI DAG task check
